I just logged in to try it (Test Server values). I bought a gold bar for about 10p5g and an opal for 17p8g. Enchanted the gold, did the combine, and sold the necklace for 29p3g. Just over 1p profit, which covers about 1 loss in 25 tries. It won't cover your learning costs, but its also a higher value selling price than buying. Assuming a 1 in 20 failure, you just barely lose money.
